@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_brbnvr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.02
    tmp = wp.exp(0.44)
    v2 = (v0 * ((v1 + 0.70 / tmp + 0.97) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.95)))
    v1 = (0.20 - wp.sin((v2 + 0.37 + tmp + 0.55)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(tmp) + 0.70)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((v0 + 0.32 + v0 + 0.66)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.53)))
    data[tid] = v0
